{"tid":2120370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"潘小濤辭職商台???","createTime":"2020-07-22T15:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T11:28:12.000Z","uid":60281,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ca9d89468055c20e28dc87d450844c0df818c379","tid":2120370,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【最新消息】資深傳媒人潘小濤辭職商台 「未來一段時間環境是艱難的」<br />\n<br />\n資深傳媒人潘小濤已向工作十多年的商業電台辭職，現時主持一周五天的早上時事評論節目《在晴朗的一天出發》，八月七日將是他在節目中最後一天與聽眾見面。潘小濤回覆查詢時坦言，對離開商台是十分不捨，今次是因個人理由辭職，與商台是保持著愉快的關係離開，他日後仍會以客席身份主持商台一些節目。但他坦言，「作為傳媒，未來一段時間環境是艱難的」。<br />\n<br />\n潘小濤說原打算本周五在節目公布辭職之消息，他強調與商台關係是很愉快的，公司對他亦很支持<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1215516128791794/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkcnews%2Fphotos%2Fa.384058221937593%2F1215516128791794%2F&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=a5e7b12e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkcnews/photos/a.384058221937593/1215516128791794/</a>"},{"pid":"21c39101537531120534d39205f7b25c1ed101c8","tid":2120370,"uid":36049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"佢放曬風話自己會移民走<br />\n唔意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbe4433e2432166436ccb71375a122f5fb0c62f","tid":2120370,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21c39101537531120534d39205f7b25c1ed101c8","tid":2120370,"uid":36049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T15:51:36.000Z","msg":"佢放曬風話自己會移民走<br />\n唔意外<img src=\"/